Carol Henry (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carol_Henry_(actor) 0 Carol Henry (July-14-1918, Oklahoma, September-17-1987, North Hollywood, Los Angeles, California) was an American character actor who played the parts of henchmen in Western films and television series throughout the 1940s, 1950s and 1960s. He also served as a stunt man in various films although all his work in that field went uncredited.He appeared in an episode of Sergeant Preston of the Yukon in 1955 as McClain, a murderer.
